psalm.text:
[[Dn 3,82]]You sons of men, bless the Lord; 
praise and exalt him above all forever.

[[Dn 3,83]]O Israel, bless the Lord; 
praise and exalt him above all forever.

[[Dn 3,84]]Priests of the Lord, bless the Lord; 
praise and exalt him above all forever.

[[Dn 3,85]]Servants of the Lord, bless the Lord; 
praise and exalt him above all forever.

[[Dn 3,86]]Spirits and souls of the just, bless the Lord; 
praise and exalt him above all forever.

[[Dn 3,87]]Holy men of humble heart, bless the Lord; 
praise and exalt him above all forever.
